Governorship (State Delegates),
State House of Assembly (LGA Delegates), will hold. On Friday, 27th of May, 2022 primary elections for Senate (LGA Delegates) will hold while House of Representatives (LGA Delegates) will hold on Saturday 28th of May, 2022. 